 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實真係無諗過<br />\n有時會同朋友一齊諗有咩可以搞<br />\n但好似香港已經好難再創業咁.."},{"pid":"56e6d7efc14dc18f631cbcc35dc8e6d474f34452","tid":113180,"uid":12070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:26:40.000Z","msg":"大把野搞 大前題 資金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17475c3bc01e36f4f8b3a4279f31656d7d7857f4","tid":113180,"uid":20892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有錢邊個想打工<br />\n無錢既 點樣唔打工丫<br />\n香港地...</blockquote><br />\n其實有時打工賺錢易過創業<br />\n創對風險大 唔一定成功<br />\n但香港地創對真係....食兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你賺到一筆錢 巴打會想做咩生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實真係無諗過<br />\n有時會同朋友一齊諗有咩可以搞<br />\n但好似香港已經好難再創業咁..</blockquote><br />\n同班朋友成日討論有咩可以搞 <br />\n呢樣得唔得 個樣得唔得<br />\n但係香港真係同外國好唔同<br />\n喺外國就算開間小店都可以足夠生活享受人生<br />\n香港唔係做金融 會被人話唔係腳踏實地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5f79943a738947d085a2b3671e54f8a932be74","tid":113180,"uid":20892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大把野搞 大前題 資金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然資金係第一步<br />\n但係好多人有左第一桶金之後 希望安全同保守<br />\n其實創業真係好需要勇氣<br />\n無錢有煩 有錢有煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果巴打有錢 會搞d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5578542e6844716f5a734967cd5b9e1eee66d47e","tid":113180,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:42:31.000Z","msg":"樓主咩背景"},{"pid":"fdd610fed0f30164b50088d86672eb5c31e322f3","tid":113180,"uid":20892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T21:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主咩背景</blockquot